text: Nind is an unincorporated community in Adair County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Nind was established in 1887, and remained in operation until 1907. The origin of the name Nind is obscure. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Adair County, Missouri Category:1887 establishments in Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Nind, Missouri
